          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "In Miami you were into real estate.  People with too much money and nt enough time to manage it would come to you. Your family connections and personal allure were all you needed to run the largest ponzi scheme and real estate fraud in Florida. Luckily for you, before the federal govenement was abel to close in on your fraudulent investments a Ventrue Elder embraced you to run his own assets.  Incredibly enough the same tactics that allowed you to keep your fake money machine running in the mortal world have served you well in the Camarilla.  You're a rising star in the Ventrue Clan and have the support and money of several well connected Ancilla and Elders in Europe.  An eager Ventrue named Hugo Valois even agreed to be your blood bonded retainer in hopes of riding your coat tails up the Ventrue ladder.  You're not sure how long this ride is going to last, but you do know that you'll have to keep funneling more and more Clan resources into your fraudulent system to keep up the illusion of stability. This has led you to move every few years to a new city and entice a new circle of investors. So far the Clan Elders assume anyone suspicious of your success is just jealous."
